         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ Michaelmas ¶ 1880 ¶  ¶ I am obliged to thank your Eminence for the favour of having informed me with handwritten notice of the first part of your learned publication about the biblical pla...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">80.09.29a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Lajos Haynald</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Magyar Természettüdományi Múseum, Budapest.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Haynald: 'Baron Muller Ferdin. | 7/10 1881. scripsi ex mihi [writings of mine]: "Parlatore," "Castenea," "Ceratophyllum", "Algae Equado[rae]".' The first three items are respectively Haynald (1879), Haynald (1881a) and Haynald (1881), copies of which are in the offprint collection at the Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne. The fourth item has not been identified; however, Haynald is known to have acquired P. Sodiro's collection of plants from Ecuador (see Ascherson (1893a), p. LIII).</p>
               </note>Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">am Michaelistage,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">1880</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es liegt mir die Pflicht ob, Ew Eminenz für die Gewogenheit zu danken, mir mit handschriftlicher Notiz den ersten Theil Ihrer gelehrten Schriften über die Bibel-Gewächse mitgetheilt zu haben. Diese wichtige Abhandlung, welche sich an die Arbeiten von Celsius, Hiller u Ursinus anschliesst, wird mir aus Ew. Eminenz eigner Hand stets ein werthvolles Souvenir bleiben.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich erlaube mir, Ihnen wieder einige meiner neuere Schriften vorzulegen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dem österreich. Schiffe, welches die Gegenstände für die Weltausstellung aus Ihrem Reiche hierher brachte, sende ich (den ersten Versuch wiederholend) einige Pflanzen der edlen <name key="Brassaia%20actinophylla">Brassaia actinophylla</name> nach Klausenburg ab, hoffend dass sich der verehrte Prof Brassai über dieses Gewächs noch recht lange freuen möge.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit ehrerbietigster Ergebenheit der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Sr Eminenz</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">dem Herrn Cardinal</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Haynald, Grosskreuz</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">&amp;c &amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Michaelmas</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1880</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am obliged to thank your Eminence for the favour of having informed me with handwritten notice of the first part of your learned publication about the biblical plants.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Haynald (1879a), in Hungarian. A separate of the item was published in the same year; Haynald (1894) is a French version.</p>
               </note> This important paper, which follows on the work of Celsius, Hiller and Ursinus,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Celsius (1745-7); Hiller (1725); Ursin (1663).</p>
               </note> will always remain for me a valuable souvenir from your Eminence's own hand.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I take the liberty of presenting you again with some of my recent publications.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the Austrian ship that brought the things here from your kingdom for the International Exhibition,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1880-1.</p>
               </note> I shall send off (repeating the first attempt) some plants of the noble <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Brassaia%20actinophylla">Brassaia actinophylla</name>
               </seg> to Klausenburg, hoping that the revered Prof. Brassai may be pleased with this plant for a long time yet.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With the most respectful devotion</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">His Eminence Cardinal Haynald</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Grosskreuz</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Brassaia%20actinophylla">Brassaia actinophylla</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
